ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.treedifferencing

类 Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.treedifferencing.Node
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Cloneable, MutableTreeNode, TreeNode

    public class Node
extends DefaultMutableTreeNode
    General tree node.

    TreeDifferencer can only apply the matching and edit script generation if the two trees are made out of such nodes.

    作者:
    Beat Fluri
    另请参阅:
    TreeDifferencer, 序列化表格
